  "term": "thm:limsup-liminf-extremal-cluster-values",
  "kind": "Theorem",
  "title": "Limsup and Liminf Are Extremal Cluster Values",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $(x_n)$ be a bounded real sequence. Then\n$\\limsup_{n\\to\\infty}x_n$ is the largest cluster value of $(x_n)$, and\n$\\liminf_{n\\to\\infty}x_n$ is the smallest cluster value of $(x_n)$.",
